WEBVTT

00:00:26.213 --> 00:00:32.386 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My parents always tell me
that they love me very much.

00:00:32.386 --> 00:00:38.142 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So I’ll be loyal to them,
and I’ll earn their trust.

00:00:38.142 --> 00:00:43.439 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ll treat them with respect
and follow all the rules

00:00:43.439 --> 00:00:48.360 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because Jehovah says
that’s what to do.

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:59.413 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When I’m loyal to Jehovah,
It makes him happy to see.

00:00:59.413 --> 00:01:10.299 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And when I’m loyal to Jehovah,
He’ll be loyal to me.

00:01:10.299 --> 00:01:16.180 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah taught me right from wrong,
so I’ll do my best

00:01:16.180 --> 00:01:21.894 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To make him happy
ev’ry time I face a test.

00:01:21.894 --> 00:01:27.149 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Others might make fun,
and some may not be kind.

00:01:27.149 --> 00:01:32.071 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But I’ll be loyal.
I’ve made up my mind.

00:01:32.071 --> 00:01:42.831 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When I’m loyal to Jehovah,
It makes him happy to see.

00:01:42.831 --> 00:01:53.842 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And when I’m loyal to Jehovah,
He’ll be loyal to me.

